{"tid":1536970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非持續付出運動的機會","createTime":"2019-09-03T18:29:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T16:32:49.000Z","uid":279332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bd12af7b5235e353c408593587e143489be40a41","tid":1536970,"uid":279332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:29:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好多和理非都想<span style=\"color: red;\">不斷為運動付出</span>，但又唔想衝或者圍警處。<br />\n其實可唔可以<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins><strong>搵個地方日日放工去坐</strong></ins></span>，去集會。叫吓口號。<br />\n甚至勇武手足傷咗，攰，都可以去集會。<br />\n<br />\n運動要長期運作落去，<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><ins>一定唔可以不斷送頭</ins></strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n地點要搵個<span style=\"color: green;\">[url]<strong><ins>四通八達</ins></strong>[/url]</span>嘅地方，大家俾啲意見。<br />\n<br />\n頭盔︰梗係唔好唔申請不反對通知書啦！<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"5073b6bcff0e83bdbeead98917a0dff857fec6a0","tid":1536970,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:30:09.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0dcd7a714ae587972ed9444a9a902209ea404dad","tid":1536970,"uid":317299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:33:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sHcuNJL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsHcuNJL.jpg&h=417a49e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不反對通知書申請中<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n9月6日 反濫捕 抗威權集會<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1535223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1535223</a>"},{"pid":"5038189ab2c82bdef0db94974318d4c4c8401fdc","tid":1536970,"uid":279332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:32:49.000Z","msg":"自 pish"}]}